Package com.chembiohub.tpmap.analysis.analysispane

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TPCorumAnalysisPane
    TPCorumAnalysisPane Create a TPAanalysis pane with a button to instantiate Corum analysis
    TPExportPane1D
    TTPPExportPane1D Export selected proteins in a 1D TPMAP analysis, parameters can be exported as a table and charts can be exported as images.
    TPExportPane2D
    TPExpertPane2D Creates a TPAnalysisPane with a button to instantiate the export of selected proteins as a table.
    TPFCPane
    TPFCPane Instantiates a TPAnalysisPane with sliders to change the default fold change values.
    TPMeanDifferencePane
    TPMeanDifferencePane Creates a TPAnalysisPane with a button to instantiate mean difference analysis
    TPStringFunctionalEnrichmentPane
    TPStringFunctionalEnrichmentPane Create a button to instantiate String functional enrichment of selected proteins.
    TPStringNetworkPane
    TPStringNetworkPane Creates a TPAnalysisPane with a button to instantiate String PPI network analysis of selected proteins
    TPTMPane
    TPTMPane Instantiates a TPAnalysisPane with a slider to change the weight of the TM shift of the 1D score.
    TPUniProtPane
    TPUniProtPane Create a TPAnalysisPane with a button to instantiate UniProt analysis
